; Medals
* [[:en:November 29|November 29]], [[:en:1889|1889]] (Meiji 22): {{ill|Constitution Promulgation Medal|ja|記念章#賞勲局所管の記念章|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Constitution Promulgation Medal|qq=}}<ref>『官報』第1935号「叙任及辞令」1889th year 12月9日。</ref>

